Nation.africa has crossed 200,000 mark in registered users in just under five months, a boost for Nation Media Group’s digital transformation programme.
The achievement cements NMG’s position among media houses on the continent that have transformed to digital brands and succeeded.
Coming at a time the media business has been disrupted, the subscriptions stamps the group’s commitment to generating content that informs, educates and entertains while keeping in mind the changing needs and trends of the industry.



