“It is a journey to empower all,” NMG Head of Development and Learning Churchill Otieno said.
“The journey is long. We urge you to be part of it.”





Nation Media Group uses Augmented Reality to launch Nation.Africa at Serena Hotel in Nairobi on September 4, 2020.
